quran[29]{c,v,t,f}:
  77,49,"Ègbé ni ní ọjọ́ yẹn fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́."
  77,50,"Nígbà náà, ọ̀rọ̀ wo ni wọn yóò gbàgbọ́ lẹ́yìn rẹ̀?{1}.",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-’A‘rọ̄f; 7:185.]
  79,40,"Ní ti ẹni tí ó páyà ìdúró níwájú Olúwa rẹ̀, tí ó tún kọ ìfẹ́-inú fún ẹ̀mí (ara rẹ̀),"
  79,41,"dájúdájú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra, òhun ni ibùgbé (rẹ̀)."
  79,42,"Wọ́n ń bi ọ́ léèrè nípa Àkókò náà pé: “Ìgbà wo l’ó máa ṣẹlẹ̀?”"
  80,37,"Ẹnì kọ̀ọ̀kan wọn ní ọjọ́ yẹn l’ó ti ní ọ̀ràn tó máa tó o ó rán."
  80,38,"Àwọn ojú kan lọ́jọ́ yẹn yóò mọ́lẹ̀."
  80,39,"Wọn yó máa rẹ́rìn-ín, wọn yó sì máa dunnú."
  83,25,"Wọn yóò máa fún wọn mu nínú ọtí onídèérí."
  83,26,"Àlùmísìkí ni (òórùn) ìparí rẹ̀. Kí àwọn alápàáǹtètè ṣàpáǹtètè nínú ìyẹn."
  83,27,"Tẹsnīm ni wọ́n yóò máa pòpọ̀ (mọ́ ọtí náà)."
  84,22,"Rárá, ńṣe ni àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ ń pè é ní irọ́."
  84,23,"Allāhu sì nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń fi pamọ́ (sínú ọkàn wọn)."
  84,24,"Nítorí náà, fún wọn ní ìró ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro."
  85,19,"Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ sì ń pe òdodo ní irọ́."
  85,20,"Allāhu sì yí wọn ká lẹ́yìn wọn."
  85,21,"Àmọ́ sá, ohun (tí A fi ránṣẹ́ sí ọ ni) al-Ƙur’ān alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé,"
  86,13,"Dájúdájú al-Ƙur’ān ni ọ̀rọ̀-ìpínyà (láààrin òdodo àti irọ́)."
  86,14,"Kì í sì ṣe àwàdà."
  86,15,"Dájúdájú wọ́n ń déte gan-an."
  87,10,"Ẹni tí ó máa páyà (Allāhu) máa lo ìrántí."
  87,11,"Olórí-burúkú sì máa takété sí i."
  87,12,"(Òun sì ni) ẹni tí ó máa wọ inú Iná tó tóbi."
  88,7,"Kò níí mú wọn sanra. Kò sì níí rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀ nínú ebi."
  88,8,"Àwọn ojú kan yó sì kún fún ìgbádùn ní ọjọ́ yẹn"
  88,9,"nítorí pé (ó) yọ́nú sí (ẹ̀san) iṣẹ́ rẹ̀."
  89,4,"Ó tún fi òru nígbà tí ó bá dé búra."
  89,5,"Ǹjẹ́ ìbúra wà nínú ìyẹn fún onílàákàyè?"
  89,6,"Ṣé o kò wòye sí bí Olúwa rẹ ti ṣe ọ̀rọ̀ ará ‘Ād,"